title: Double Honey Haloumi & Turkish-Style Fattoush Salad with Radish & Garlic Dip
description: This salad sensation will take you on a culinary adventure straight to the heart of the Middle East! Crunchy veggies, crispy tortilla
chips and golden haloumi kissed by a drizzle of sticky honey all come together for a fresh and flavourful meal.
